This recipe is definitely real German potato salad, not the fake stuff they sell in the supermarket. It is the only way to go. One thing I did do, I had a lot to do when I was making it as I was preparing for a large party. Julia Child has this thing about slicing the potatoes before cooking them for French style potato salad. I tried it. It saves tons of time because the potatoes cook in 5-10 minutes. You do not hurt your hands handling hot potatoes. Plus, the potatoes are ready to dress when cooked. Try it.

