To those annoyed with the bacon frying: Bake it in the oven at 350 - 375 degrees for about 20 minutes. Check it about 10 minutes into it or when you begion to smell it and then every 2 minutes or so thereafter. It browns quickly at the end. There is virtually no mess, it is incredibly easy and the bacon comes out beautifully!

